descriptionNullable:
This is a small dataset of wildlife derived from research partners at the Wild Chimpanzee Foundation and the Max Planck Institute for Evolutionary Anthropology which uses these camera trap images to capture wildlife for conservation research purposes. This was downloaded from Driven Data website and manipulated for better processing and uploaded to kaggle in order to more easily work on the dataset within a team. 

For more information, please see the link to Driven Data and support them and their great efforts:

https://www.drivendata.org/competitions/87/competition-image-classification-wildlife-conservation/page/483/
